    <h1 class="cs-hero-title">18 STEPS TO 4 — THE GOLDEN FLOW</h1>
    <p class="cs-hero-desc">Redesigning crypto wallet onboarding for emerging markets. A 77.8% step reduction that made the difference between users finishing and users leaving.</p>
    <div class="cs-hero-meta">
